{"tid":1596766,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牙侵新國安顧問係極度反中派","createTime":"2019-09-26T15:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T01:10:02.000Z","uid":33359,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"555d8fc10af0048138f3d5150de333df3d9914be","tid":1596766,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjWrbwC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjWrbwC.png&h=4cf59fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這位是白宮新任副國安顧問叫作 Matt Pottinger，或譯博明，之前是白宮的亞洲政策顧<br />\n問。<br />\n<br />\n現在當上美國國安二把手，是川普故意擺上來施壓中國的猛將。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n博明的履歷很漂亮，University of Massachusetts Amherst 中國研究畢業，而且講得一<br />\n口流利的華語。畢業後在《路透社》與《華爾街日報》駐北京和香港記者長達七年，是超<br />\n級中國通。<br />\n<br />\n不當記者後，博明先在海軍陸戰隊服役，接著加入政府，成為華府中國專家，而且他還是<br />\n個友台派。<br />\n<br />\n這在華府其實不常見，美國國策過去沒有非常針對中國，即使是中國事務的鷹派，對台灣<br />\n友善的白宮人士也不多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但這就是博明最特別的地方。<br />\n<br />\n他因為報導中國貪腐，曾經被中共人員跟拍、強迫把筆記沖進馬桶，還遭到北京國安毆打<br />\n（直接往臉上揍），甚至被拘捕過。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在博明辭職記者以後的文章中，曾提到被揍臉那次，涉及一樁中國偷賣核燃料的事件，參<br />\n見〈Mightier Than the Pen〉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為有這些經歷，博明非常嫌棄中共的腐敗與殘暴，北京看到這樁新人事案應該都在皮皮<br />\n挫。<br />\n<br />\n不只對中很兇，友台的博明3月曾與台灣外交部次長徐斯儉出現在索羅門群島，助台灣鞏<br />\n固邦交。<br />\n<br />\n在朝鮮、香港、印太戰略等方面，博明都涉入甚深。例如三次「川金會」背後規劃者，就<br />\n是博明。在美中貿易戰中，博明則扮演重要幕僚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身為白宮副國安顧問，博明跟國安顧問 Robert O&rsquo;Brien 立場一致。他跟另一個鷹派中<br />\n國通，國務院主管亞太事務助理國務卿 David Stilwell（史迪威）也很熟。<br />\n<br />\n美國的外交政策向來是白宮與國務院雙核心，現在亞太事務助理國務卿、國安顧問、副國<br />\n安顧問連成一線，而且這些人都是對中大鷹派。這樣看來就算台灣不起飛，至少北京也要<br />\n慘兮兮啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1569508457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1569508457&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAwwuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=6e11538c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1569508457</a>"},{"pid":"9c8315a648082f25d97aff0536f8ba721db3db86","tid":1596766,"uid":259329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:47:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1491e7c41104fc1971dc1038efdf6d604bad37d1","tid":1596766,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4539a4350ac37172eeaf80c0e868546f882683ee","tid":1596766,"uid":87723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"this way sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c48311bb2cd19af38c7cd109b726138d674a6f","tid":1596766,"uid":193215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"Sir, this way <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2240bf57b6b35f62ffcff9a3b5cc5253b4a4cdf","tid":1596766,"uid":1372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:50:53.000Z","msg":"之前聽梁錦祥提過佢，好似已經講話佢極可能做其中一任侵嘅國安顧問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efd9552de62f2dee291fbd7db4cab89ce942758","tid":1596766,"uid":176116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"sir, this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9762dae48fbb915700f951724e66e032fb0c9ec","tid":1596766,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"本身果個應該鷹過佢囉"},{"pid":"3e54a60e7a35453af16da2a681e5eccde99d323d","tid":1596766,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:52:21.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第六期牆紙］ 百日抗爭運動，願榮光終歸香港<br />\n第六期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1583745/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/158374